thread.title: Israel admits bombing suspected Syrian nuclear reactor in 2007

title: Israel admits bombing suspected Syrian nuclear reactor in 2007
text:
Israel admits bombing suspected Syrian nuclear reactor in 2007 Wednesday, March 21, 2018 - 01:29 
Israel for the first time admitted that it bombed a suspected Syrian nuclear reactor in 2007 and said on Wednesday the strike should be a warning to Iran that it would not be allowed to develop nuclear weapons. Emily Wither reports.
